When asked the question, “Would participation in the
STEM Pathways set PTHSD students apart when applying
to your school?”, colleges responded with the following:
SUNY Binghamton: “Yes. We are a R1 research institution
and students with a strong STEM curriculum that includes
research or lab work are generally more competitive in our
applicant pool and more success as students at
Binghamton because of their early HS experience.”
